# Spec-First Workflow

- PRDs must state problem, goals, non-goals, acceptance criteria, risks, and unit testing requirements.
- Specs must include architecture, module boundaries, Pydantic contracts, edge cases, security, observability, and tests.
- Keep implementation decisions consistent with Deep Agents, LangGraph, LangChain, and Agent Skills primitives.
- Do not remove edge cases to simplify implementation.
- Treat docs as the contract future agents must implement against.

